high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the right bathroom sink
Open the left cabinet below the right sink and pick up the green spray bottle
Turn around and walk to the opposite side of the toilet and turn back to face it
Put the spray bottle on top of the back of the toilet
Walk a few feet to the left then turn right and walk forward to the trash bin
Pick up the green spray bottle from the trash bin
Turn around and walk back over to the left side of the toilet
Put the spray bottle on top of the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put the green spray bottles on the toilet

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink to your right.
Grab the cleaner from the cabinet below the sink.
Turn left and bring the cleaner to the toilet to your left.
Place the cleaner on top of the toilet.
Walk to the basket to your left.
Grab the cleaner from the basket.
Turn around and bring the cleaner to the toilet to your left.
Place the cleaner next to the other cleaner.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles of cleaning spray o the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward a step, turn right, go forward to the toilet paper holder, turn left, go to the right sink.
Take the green spray bottle from the left cabinet under the sink.
Turn left, go forward a step, turn left at the sink, go forward, turn left after passing the toilet, go forward to the wall, turn left.
Put the bottle on the toilet tank.
Turn left, go forward to the tub, turn right, go forward to the trash bin.
Take the green spray bottle from the trash bin.
Turn around, go forward, turn left after passing the toilet, go forward, turn left to face the toilet.
Put the bottle on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on a toilet's tank.
